.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
House: cape-cod, cottage, colonial, modern
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the egyptian is the social-worker##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the cottage house is the writer##1
 6. the modern house is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the italian##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the british##1
10. the owner of the dog is the colonial house##1
11. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| House      | cape-cod | colonial   | modern    | cottage      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

