.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, polish, australian, chinese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the australian is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the polish is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the egyptian is on the left or right of the polish##3
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the egyptian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the polish##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| Nationality     | chinese     | australian      | polish     | egyptian |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

