There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cauliflower, orange
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, game, davidoff, cain
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, german, indian
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 5. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 6. the cain-smoker is between the german and the game-smoker##2
 7. the davidoff-smoker is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the colombian is on the far right##1
10. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | iced-tea    | 7up       | tea       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
| Cigar   | siglo | davidoff        | cain    | game   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | german      | indian    | colombian |

