 2. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking juice is the person playing snooker##1
