 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
